com.google.gcloud.datastore

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gcloud.datastore.PartialEntity
      • com.google.gcloud.datastore.Entity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class Entity
extends PartialEntity
    An entity is the Google Cloud Datastore persistent data object. An entity holds one or more properties, represented by a name (as String) and a value (as Value), and is associated with a Key. For a list of possible values see Value.Type. This class is immutable.
    See Also:
    Google Cloud Datastore Entities, Properties, and Keys, Serialized Form
